  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Clean Minimalism\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Clean Minimalism\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"bg-slate-50 w-[1024px] h-[768px] overflow-hidden flex flex-col font-sans text-slate-900 border-8 border-slate-200\\\">\\n  <!-- Top Header Navigation -->\\n  <header class=\\\"bg-white border-b border-slate-200 px-8 py-4 flex justify-between items-center\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 rounded flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold\\\">C</div>\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-lg font-bold tracking-tight uppercase text-slate-800\\\">Collection Territory Intelligence System</h1>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"text-right\\\">\\n      <p class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-400 font-semibold\\\">Generated At</p>\\n      <p class=\\\"text-xs font-mono text-slate-600\\\">2023-10-24T14:30:00Z</p>\\n    </div>\\n  </header>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex gap-6 p-6 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Left Column: Customer & Context -->\\n    <div class=\\\"w-1/3 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <section class=\\\"bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold mb-4\\\">Detail Nasabah</h2>\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-3\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500\\\">Nama Nasabah</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"font-semibold\\\">Budi Santoso</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500\\\">ID Nasabah</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"font-mono text-sm\\\">CUST-99281-JKT</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500\\\">Alamat</p>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700 italic\\\">Jl. Kemang Raya No. 15, Jakarta Selatan, 12730</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n\\n      <section class=\\\"bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex-1 flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold mb-4\\\">Executive Summary</h2>\\n        <p class=\\\"text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          Kolektor <span class=\\\"font-bold text-blue-700\\\">KOLU</span> diidentifikasi sebagai pilihan terbaik dengan skor <span class=\\\"font-bold\\\">92/100</span>. Hal ini didasarkan pada kepadatan aktivitas historis dalam radius 1km (area inti) yang sangat tinggi (152 poin). Meskipun terdapat risiko beban kerja yang mendekati kapasitas maksimal, konsistensi kunjungan mingguannya yang stabil (CV 0.21) menjadikannya pilihan paling andal dibandingkan kandidat lain. Rekomendasi ini memiliki tingkat kepercayaan <span class=\\\"text-green-600 font-bold uppercase\\\">High</span>.\\n        </p>\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-slate-100\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 uppercase font-bold mb-2\\\">Analysis Period</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs font-medium\\\">01 Jan 2023 - 30 Sep 2023</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </section>\\n    </div>\\n\\n    <!-- Right Column: Results & Matrix -->\\n    <div class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col gap-6\\\">\\n      <!-- Top Collectors Grid -->\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden\\\">\\n        <table class=\\\"w-full text-left border-collapse\\\">\\n          <thead class=\\\"bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200\\\">\\n            <tr>\\n              <th class=\\\"px-4 py-3 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-400\\\">Rank</th>\\n              <th class=\\\"px-4 py-3 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-400\\\">Collector</th>\\n              <th class=\\\"px-4 py-3 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-400\\\">Score</th>\\n              <th class=\\\"px-4 py-3 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-400\\\">Confidence</th>\\n              <th class=\\\"px-4 py-3 text-[10px] uppercase font-bold text-slate-400\\\">Distance</th>\\n            </tr>\\n          </thead>\\n          <tbody class=\\\"text-sm\\\">\\n            <tr class=\\\"border-b border-slate-100 bg-blue-50/30\\\">\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-bold text-blue-600\\\">#1</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4\\\">KOLU-21</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-mono font-bold\\\">92</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-green-100 text-green-700 rounded text-[10px] font-bold\\\">HIGH</span></td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-mono\\\">0.42 km</td>\\n            </tr>\\n            <tr class=\\\"border-b border-slate-100\\\">\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-bold text-slate-400\\\">#2</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4\\\">KOBE-44</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-mono\\\">85</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 rounded text-[10px] font-bold\\\">MEDIUM</span></td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-mono\\\">1.15 km</td>\\n            </tr>\\n            <tr>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-bold text-slate-400\\\">#3</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4\\\">KOAN-09</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-mono\\\">78</td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-yellow-100 text-yellow-700 rounded text-[10px] font-bold\\\">MEDIUM</span></td>\\n              <td class=\\\"px-4 py-4 font-mono\\\">2.80 km</td>\\n            </tr>\\n          </tbody>\\n        </table>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Metric Detail & Action -->\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-6 flex-1\\\">\\n        <section class=\\\"bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold mb-3\\\">Risk Analysis</h2>\\n          <ul class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-red-500\\\">\342\227\217</span> Potential overload for primary collector (High active customer count).\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-yellow-500\\\">\342\227\217</span> Area periphery observation: Secondary collector has low consistency.\\n            </li>\\n            <li class=\\\"flex gap-2 text-xs text-slate-600\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-blue-500\\\">\342\227\217</span> Data recency: 15% of historical data is older than 180 days.\\n            </li>\\n          </ul>\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold mt-6 mb-3\\\">Recommended Actions</h2>\\n          <div class=\\\"space-y-2\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"p-2 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded text-[11px] text-slate-700\\\">\\n              Assign <strong>KOLU-21</strong> as Primary Collector.\\n            </div>\\n            <div class=\\\"p-2 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded text-[11px] text-slate-700\\\">\\n              Monitor <strong>KOBE-44</strong> as Backup for radius overflow.\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </section>\\n        \\n        <section class=\\\"bg-white p-5 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold mb-3\\\">Coverage Observation</h2>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-100 rounded flex items-center justify-center border border-dashed border-slate-300 relative overflow-hidden\\\">\\n             <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-4\\\">\\n               <p class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 mb-1\\\">Territory Map Preview</p>\\n               <p class=\\\"text-[10px] text-slate-400 italic font-mono\\\">Lat: -6.2731 / Lng: 106.8106</p>\\n             </div>\\n             <div class=\\\"w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"mt-3\\\">\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-slate-500\\